{"id":"guide/browser-support","title":"瀏覽器支援","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"browser-support\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4kdi5razdf2rr2s146m9cpxqe\">瀏覽器支援<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/browser-support#browser-support\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"41nh008sgrus836tf1ndn2cbk\">Angular 支援大多數常用瀏覽器，包括下列版本：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e5k6nj4n8sj4kanfrmjqhlggj\">瀏覽器</th>\n<th align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2qtb4tc6t0n06c9nurtsxj9qt\">支援的版本</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"90uu4i5p0ervrs5kpuj3irbn8\">Chrome</td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"10nx2syjqls8p69umks2dzl95\">最近的 2 個版本</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"700qkytcb5orzru854md002sp\">Firefox</td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"agh2xwz6aypbrlcoo1b61gzzp\">最新和擴充套件支援版本（ESR）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"djac3064b4nqaqm29iz4gfku6\">Edge</td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4xx9m031jhbdq2cpzj3ndy2ef\">最近的 2 個主要版本</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4sctpqy9f3lnpcim24bmprihs\">Safari</td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4xx9m031jhbdq2cpzj3ndy2ef\">最近的 2 個主要版本</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1nek5eev88y67ss32lz59n4rv\">iOS</td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4xx9m031jhbdq2cpzj3ndy2ef\">最近的 2 個主要版本</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dr3y0bktyp2tf07cm9wloc8z1\">Android</td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4xx9m031jhbdq2cpzj3ndy2ef\">最近的 2 個主要版本</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ce6jbiiyw6r8sfyixso25wfvr\">Angular 的持續整合過程會在每次 Pull Request 時透過 <a href=\"https://saucelabs.com\">Sauce Labs</a> 在所有瀏覽器上執行本框架的單元測試。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"polyfills\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"94rv7a89hq733vz1np8fg9i2b\">膩子指令碼（polyfill）<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/browser-support#polyfills\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"36ix1zwkla89146f3oxwv09xu\">Angular CLI提供對polyfills的支援。 建立新專案時，CLI還會建立一個\n<code>src/polyfills.ts</code>檔案。 如果你的應用程式需要任何polyfills，你可以將它們新增到\n<code>src/polyfills.ts</code>檔案中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"96m7sdo973juakqpxpfdlykeg\">如果你不使用CLI來建立專案，請參見\n<a href=\"guide/browser-support#non-cli\">非CLI使用者的Polyfills</a>部分。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9j6v9mr0ob39zpovw0dfkqv1b\">如果為自定義polyfill建立一個TypeScript檔案，請確保將其包含在\n<code>tsconfig</code>檔案的\n<code>files</code>屬性中。</p>\n<code-example language=\"jsonc\" syntax=\"jsonc\">\n\n{\n  \"extends\": \"./tsconfig.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    ...\n  },\n  \"files\": [\n    \"src/main.ts\",\n    \"src/polyfills.ts\"\n  ]\n  ...\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p><a id=\"non-cli\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"polyfills-for-non-cli-users\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7hjlg36n349jqnemuxqjl59fu\">非 CLI 的使用者的膩子指令碼<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/browser-support#polyfills-for-non-cli-users\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dek3bn4ehera5ojiaq1lnb11l\">如果你不使用 CLI，就要直接把膩子指令碼新增到宿主頁（<code>index.html</code>）中，就像這樣：。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4reizjf10jcs1ftw359bt1ndz\">比如：</p>\n<code-example header=\"src/index.html\" language=\"html\">\n\n&lt;!-- pre-zone polyfills --&gt;\n&lt;script src=\"node_modules/core-js/client/shim.min.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;script&gt;\n  /**\n   * you can configure some zone flags which can disable zone interception for some\n   * asynchronous activities to improve startup performance - use these options only\n   * if you know what you are doing as it could result in hard to trace down bugs.\n   */\n  // __Zone_disable_requestAnimationFrame = true; // disable patch requestAnimationFrame\n  // __Zone_disable_on_property = true; // disable patch onProperty such as onclick\n  // __zone_symbol__UNPATCHED_EVENTS = ['scroll', 'mousemove']; // disable patch specified eventNames\n  /*\n   * in Edge developer tools, the addEventListener will also be wrapped by zone.js\n   * with the following flag, it will bypass `zone.js` patch for Edge.\n   */\n  // __Zone_enable_cross_context_check = true;\n&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;!-- zone.js required by Angular --&gt;\n&lt;script src=\"node_modules/zone.js/bundles/zone.umd.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;!-- application polyfills --&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Fri Nov 04 2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/platform-browser\n - guide/architecture-next-steps\n - guide/build\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/npm-packages\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/browser-support#browser-support\n - guide/browser-support#non-cli\n - guide/browser-support#polyfills\n - guide/browser-support#polyfills-for-non-cli-users\n - https://saucelabs.com\n-->"}